<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <meta name="theme-color" content="#000000">
  <title>On August 13th 2021, Neverthink Shut Down</title>
  <meta name="title" content="On August 13th 2021, Neverthink Shut Down">
  <meta name="description" content="After four amazing years and a millions of views Neverthink says goodbye.">
  <meta property="og:type" content="website">
  <meta property="og:url" content="https://neverthink.tv/">
  <meta property="og:title" content="On August 13th 2021, Neverthink Shut Down">
  <meta property="og:description" content="After four amazing years and a millions of views Neverthink says goodbye.">
  <meta property="og:image" content="https://neverthink.tv/img/background-logo.png">
  <meta property="twitter:card" content="summary_large_image">
  <meta property="twitter:url" content="https://neverthink.tv/">
  <meta property="twitter:title" content="On August 13th 2021, Neverthink Shut Down">
  <meta property="twitter:description" content="After four amazing years and a millions of views Neverthink says goodbye.">
  <meta property="twitter:image" content="https://neverthink.tv/img/background-logo.png">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="css/normalize.css"/>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="css/style.css"/>
  <script src="js/splash.js"/>
  <link rel="icon" href="img/favicon.ico" type="image/x-icon">
</head>
<body>
  <div id='splash'>
    <canvas id='splashCanvas'></canvas>
    <div class='logoContainer'>
      <img class="logo" src="img/neverthink-logo-black.svg" alt="logo">
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="awards">
    <img src="img/award-1.png" alt="award 1" />
    <img src="img/award-2.png" alt="award 2" />
    <img src="img/award-3.png" alt="award 3" />
    <img src="img/award-4.png" alt="award 4" />
  </div>
  <div class="section">
    <h2>Time to say goodbye ðŸ‘‹</h2>
    <p class="large">
      We've had an incredible time building Neverthink, but our journey has now come to an end. We hope you enjoyed watching Neverthink as much as we did creating it.
    </p>
  </div>
  <div class="section">
    <h2>Stats</h2>
    <div class="stats">
      <div><h3 class="c1">15M</h3><p>Users wordwide</p></div>
      <div><h3 class="c2">85K</h3><p>Creators</p></div>
      <div><h3 class="c1">300</h3><p>Partners</p></div>
      <div><h3 class="c3">700M</h3><p>Total video views</p></div>
      <div><h3 class="c3">5M</h3><p>Videos reviewed by our&nbsp;team</p></div>
      <div><h3 class="c2">500K</h3><p>Videos selected by our&nbsp;team</p></div>
    </div>

  </div>
  <div class="section section-spacious">
    <a href="https://memeinsider.com/releases/the-state-of-the-video-meme-industry" class="quote">
      <span class="quote-text">With strong backing of people who truly love and understand meme culture. Neverthink is poised to become a major player in the world of memes</span>
      <span class="quote-source">Meme Insider</span>
    </a>
    <a href="https://www.forbes.com/sites/jacksonweimer/2021/05/27/the-new-video-platform-for-watching-high-quality-memes-neverthinktv/?sh=55b0b33e32ab" class="quote">
      <span class="quote-text">The New Video Platform For Watching High-Quality Memes: Neverthink.TV</span>
      <span class="quote-source">Forbes</span>
    </a>
  </div>
  <div class="section">
    <h2>The team</h2>
    <div class="grid">
      {% for user in team | sort(false, false, 'name') %}
        <div class="grid-item">
          <img class="grid-image" src="{{ user.image }}" alt="{{ user.name }}"/>
          <span class="grid-name">{{ user.name }}</span>
          <span class="grid-title">{{ user.title }}</span>
        </div>
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="section">
    <h2>Our partners</h2>
    <div class="grid">
      {% for user in partners | sort(false, false, 'name') %}
        <div class="grid-item">
          <img class="grid-image" src="{{ user.profileImageUrl }}" alt="{{ user.publicName }}"/>
          <span class="grid-name">{{ user.publicName }}</span>
        </div>
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
  </div>
  <p class="footer">Made with â™¥ in Finland</p>
  <script>
    const splash = new Splash('splashCanvas', 32, splashColorSets.brand)

    function resizeSplash() {
      const splashContainer = document.getElementById('splash')
      splash.resize(splashContainer.offsetWidth, splashContainer.offsetHeight)
    }

    function init() {
      window.onresize = resizeSplash
      resizeSplash()
    }

    init()
  </script>
</body>
</html>